node.contents: I found adding the following to progaurd-rules.pro when using guava worked for me: `-dontwarn sun.misc.Unsafe -dontwarn com.google.common.**`

astNode.text: I found adding the following to progaurd-rules.pro when using guava worked for me: `-dontwarn sun.misc.Unsafe -dontwarn com.google.common.**`

node.contents: Using Maven in my case, google-api-client brought guava-jdk5 as a dependency, causing similar problems.
